<p>This is really terrific. Sorry I didn’t get to comment on the draft, but I don’t think it needed it. I love the cleverly-constructed technobabble, the braided plot, the brisk but vivid character work, the references - all of it. This is a worthy companion to the Antimemetics series.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>This system is able to detect and perceive unsecured info-streams that include information about itself. Whenever (and wherever) this information is detected an incursion occurs</p>
</blockquote>
<p>New headcanon: SCP-2521 is simply another facet/incarnation of 3125. After all, 2+5+2+1 = 5+5, or in reverse it’s 125<sup>2</sup>.</p>

