<p>I am really glad that you, ARD and qntm all enjoyed this, it is always a risk when you use someone else's characters that you will get them wrong.</p>
<p>Speaking of which I need to ask you a question about the current state of the Sagrada Familia (which will make an appearance in part IV). Expect a PM soon.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>New headcanon: SCP-2521 is simply another facet/incarnation of 3125. After all, 2+5+2+1 = 5+5, or in reverse it’s 1252.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Yeah that's certainly possible, and the fact that it appears to made of dead memes in the form of VHS actually fits into the way that the metaphysics works here. I definitely will think about this.</p>

